headline: Arch Capital: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: PEMBROKE, Bermuda (AP) — Arch Capital Group Ltd. (ACGL) on Tuesday reported second-quarter net income of $1.24 billion. The Pembroke, Bermuda-based company said it had net income of $3.23 per share. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring gains, were $2.58 per share.
